name: MITSUBISHI 3000GT VR-4
description: The Mitsubishi 3000GT VR-4 is a high-performance sports car produced from 1990 to 1999, featuring a twin-turbocharged 3.0-liter V6 engine producing 320 horsepower and 315 lb-ft of torque, paired with a 5-speed manual transmission and all-wheel drive. The VR-4 trim level was the top-of-the-line model, offering advanced features such as active aerodynamics, adaptive damping, and a sport-tuned suspension. With its impressive performance capabilities and advanced technology, the 3000GT VR-4 is a sought-after model among sports car enthusiasts and collectors.
rate: The overall rating of the Mitsubishi 3000GT VR-4 is around 8.5 out of 10

name: MITSUBISHI DIAMANTE LS
description: The Mitsubishi Diamante LS is a mid-size luxury sedan produced from 1990 to 2005, known for its sleek design, spacious interior, and robust performance. The Diamante LS is often praised for its value for money, offering a premium driving experience at a relatively affordable price point.
rate: The overall rating of the Mitsubishi Diamante LS is around 7.5 out of 10

name: MITSUBISHI ECLIPSE CROSS SEL
description: The Mitsubishi Eclipse Cross SEL is a compact luxury crossover SUV that offers a perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology. It features a 1.5-liter turbocharged engine, producing 152 horsepower, and comes equipped with advanced safety features like forward collision mitigation, lane departure warning, and blind-spot monitoring. The SEL trim also boasts premium amenities, including heated leather seats, a panoramic sunroof, and a touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration.
rate: The overall rating of the 2024 Mitsubishi Eclipse Cross SEL is around 8.2 out of 10

name: MITSUBISHI ECLIPSE GT

rate: The overall rating of the Mitsubishi Eclipse GT is around 8.0 out of 10

name: MITSUBISHI LANCER GT 2.4

name: MITSUBISHI MIRAGE SE

name: MITSUBISHI OUTLANDER SEL PREMIUM
description: The Mitsubishi Outlander SEL Premium is a mid-size SUV that offers a spacious interior, comfortable ride, and advanced safety features, including a 360-degree camera system, adaptive cruise control, and lane departure warning.
